r dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gbouhier/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/573693695f8f74504c93563cade9468d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/573693695f8f74504c93563cade9468d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gbouhier/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gbouhier</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 24, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi really enjoy this plugin, it fits perfectly for many cases and is perfectly integrated with Geodirectory &amp; GetPaid (plugins from the same developers).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The support is very reactive and get your back anytime !</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br />Recommended 100% </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice layout and easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dllaskey/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec60dcfd617d7c98ea63b737f7b3fbda?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec60dcfd617d7c98ea63b737f7b3fbda?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dllaskey/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dllaskey</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 15, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Great widgets to customize profile and other pages. Nice layout too!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I had a couple of questions and customer services was prompt and very helpful</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Brilliant Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lmccutcheonlw2/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46f3fcddf318c8deb82187f5402cc39b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46f3fcddf318c8deb82187f5402cc39b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lmccutcheonlw2/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lmccutcheonlw2</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 21, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have been using this product on my web directory and the support is 5 stars.  The team are always getting back to me within 24 hours which is critical as a small business owner.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Great job guys.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Quick Efficient Assistance</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/inlandscene/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42f66984c083064258d3df6299db6281?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42f66984c083064258d3df6299db6281?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/inlandscene/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">inlandscene</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 14, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I appreciate the quick and efficient assistance I received from Rahul Gandhi. He held my hand and guided me step by step on how to fix something I messed up. My UsersWP form wasn\'t allowing people to register. It was because I added multiple duplicate fields. Didn\'t even know I had. LOL Appreciate the great customer service. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">excellent (and patient!) support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zaphod71/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5105b311831700405af9f91ec8b963d3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5105b311831700405af9f91ec8b963d3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zaphod71/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zaphod71</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 10, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ever had \'support\' that seem to do and say anything to avoid helping you? These guys are the complete opposite. Can\'t thank them enough.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lightboxes not functioning properly with my Liquido THeme</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/berrybok/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69d71ca28769104c288af5341c039976?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69d71ca28769104c288af5341c039976?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/berrybok/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">berrybok</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 13, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It took a few days to iterate through the better approach but your rep stuck with it until the issue was resolved. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">We added the following CSS in Appearance-&gt;Customise-&gt;Additional CSS:<br />.modal.fade { opacity: 1; }</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:96:\"Light weight Front-end login form, User Registration, User Profile and Members Directory plugin.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:57:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/userswp.1.2.22.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:1:{s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:93:\"<ul>\n<li>New settings screen, all addons will need to be updated - BREAKING CHANGE</li>\n</ul>\";}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:60:\"https://ps.w.org/userswp/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2784318\";s:7:\"caption\";s:18: