>\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Well</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/beaversden/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6eccc86500be71226eba5a48918d06c6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6eccc86500be71226eba5a48918d06c6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/beaversden/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Glenn R Beaver Jr. <small>(beaversden)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Anything that makes Gutenberg better is great in my book</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pretty good for basic stuff.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/countzeroor/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/adb78853a0518fb6e3e22fff167ecd95?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/adb78853a0518fb6e3e22fff167ecd95?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/countzeroor/\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(CountZeroOR)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is very easy to use, and allows me to create stock calls to action for my posts (Patreon and Ko-Fi links, that sort of thing), along with some reasonable formatting.\n\nI haven\'t particularly done anything complicated with the software yet, so we\'ll see how things go when if I end up doing something more involved later. I may revisit this review at that time.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chopperbell/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55281bbfcc737a8edf6eaa3f454b10cc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55281bbfcc737a8edf6eaa3f454b10cc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chopperbell/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tunglin <small>(chopperbell)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 5, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">good</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">An excellent plugin with a great support team</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lilleulven/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f70ead1f97ef432dc0bb0b0fb1742077?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f70ead1f97ef432dc0bb0b0fb1742077?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lilleulven/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lilleulven</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I installed Easy Blocks because I needed a way to get subtitles working, without using the standard title blocks. After some time searching for a plugin that could do the work and would not fail with Gutenberg, I came over Easy Blocks, and it looked \"good enough\" to do the job. \nTrying it, yes, it does what it promises. \nHowever, I stumbled over two minor \"problems\" along the way. For one I had a workaround, but an official solution would have been nice, for the other well I could have lived with it. Anyway, I figured to contact the support via the chat function on the website. Within minutes I had someone to chat with, who promised to look into it, and within two hours I had an email with the solutions for my problems (one will be fixed with a new block being released potentially next week). \n\nSo thumbs up for this plugin/Gutenberg extension and the team around it!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great addition to my Gutenberg Editor</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/infinite1potential/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/afa0145d4c468f79708087828f6ebe55?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/afa0145d4c468f79708087828f6ebe55?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/infinite1potential/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">infinite1potential</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I love all my Gutenberg plugins that I am using.  I\'m looking forward to see what new is developed.  Even a beginner like me can use this without difficulty.\nI am grateful for these.  It has been a real mindset change and learning curve going from Microsoft FrontPage2000 working in tables for years until it finally became so outdated I had to find something else.  I did a lot of looking and come up with I had best learn WordPress if I wanted to do much with building websites.  I have 5 I had to get done fast once I wrapped my mind around changing my old hosting over to the cPanel.  I am so glad I did.  Less expensive and so much easier to use.  I didn\'t have to go into my old hosting very much with FrontPage2000. I did it on my computer and uploaded it. With WordPress it really makes a difference.  I had a month to get this done.  You old pros are probably getting a chuckle out of this.  \nLove my Gutenberg plugins.  Thanks so much.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Working well</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petisk/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/696979238ce763ca06cd8bd11009b352?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/696979238ce763ca06cd8bd11009b352?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petisk/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">petisk</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Working well</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/earid/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/43fb404d20915d7152c62b74e682d8a3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/43fb404d20915d7152c62b74e682d8a3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/earid/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Earid A. <small>(earid)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 13, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A helpful plugin. Best Plugin for Gutenberg user like me.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:131:\"Master Blocks is a powerful WordPress Gutenberg blocks plugin that helps you to create beautiful pages in default WordPress Editor.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/ultimate-bloc